esign-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary kitchen with pastel cabinets, open shelving, and marble backsplash; adjacent bookshelf and a green partition under wooden ceiling beams.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576383\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576383\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern dining area with a round table, wooden chairs, a vase of flowers, a large black-and-white cityscape photograph, and wood-paneled walls and ceiling.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0