g 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576386\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576386\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bathroom with a white vanity, terrazzo countertop, rectangular mirror, and potted plants in clay pots against light pink walls.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576387\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576387\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern wooden staircase with open risers, black metal railing, and a textured wooden wall panel alongside the stairs.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA sculptural staircase crafted in blackened steel connects the two levels and creates a dynamic juxtaposition to the natural woods. It anchors the interior, drawing the eye and reinforcing the home’s verticality.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576388\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576388\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-14-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom with a bed, gray closet, small red stool, and sliding glass door opening to a patio with wooden stairs and potted plant.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-14-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-14-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-14-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe exterior of Redwood House plays a crucial role in the overall experience, and landscape designer Monica Viarengo was enlisted to reimagine the outdoor spaces with equal thought. Her design begins at the entry courtyard. As visitors move through the property – up into the private courtyard and down toward the terraced back garden – the planting scheme shifts from curated and orderly to wild and expressive.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576389\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576389\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with a white oval bathtub, a pink towel, a small orange side table with a plant, sheer curtains, and an open sliding door to a terrace.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576390\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576390\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A modern outdoor patio with a white wire table and chairs, a large potted plant, wooden panel walls, and a staircase leading up.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe newly reclad facades, now wrapped in irregular planks of western red cedar, unify the home’s visual identity. The wood’s varied grain and tone work organically with the landscape, allowing the house to age gracefully, much like a natural element in its own habitat.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576391\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576391\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern courtyard with wooden exterior walls, an open staircase, potted greenery, large windows, and a blue wall in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576392\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576392\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A small backyard patio with a wooden fence, a metal table and two chairs, potted plants, and trees in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=576393\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-576393\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Wildflowers grow in the foreground of a garden, with a modern house, patio, and white chairs visible through open glass doors in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/05/Redwood-House-San-Francesco-Studio-Terpeluk-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on the Redwood House or Studio Terpeluk, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.studioterpeluk.com/redwood-house\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003estudioterpeluk.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/joefletcherphoto/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eJoe Fletcher\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
